{"generated":"2026-03-30T05:18:23.725655978Z","published":"2024-01-01T10:52:40Z","app":"watchexec","version":"1.25.0","notes":"<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Software development often involves running the same commands over and over. Boring! Watchexec is a simple, standalone tool that watches a path and runs a command whenever it detects modifications. Install it today with <a href=\"https://github.com/cargo-bins/cargo-binstall\"><code class=\"notranslate\">cargo-binstall watchexec-cli</code></a>, from the binaries below, find it <a href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/blob/main/doc/packages.md\">in your favourite package manager</a>, or build it from source with <code class=\"notranslate\">cargo install watchexec-cli</code>.</em></p>\n<h4 dir=\"auto\">In this release:</h4>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Startup performance improvements reducing the amount of directories visited when discovering ignore files. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1944753518\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/663\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/pull/663/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/pull/663\">#663</a> by <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/t3hmrman/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/t3hmrman\">@t3hmrman</a>)</li>\n<li>Improvements to handling of nested ignore files. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2057577042\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/745\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/issues/745/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/745\">#745</a> by <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/thislooksfun/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/thislooksfun\">@thislooksfun</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 dir=\"auto\">Other changes:</h4>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Project origin detection tweaked a little to avoid some false positives. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2061286071\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/748\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/pull/748/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/pull/748\">#748</a>)</li>\n</ul>","downloads":[{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/v1.25.0/watchexec-1.25.0-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb","filename":"watchexec-1.25.0-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb","size":2120644,"format":{"short":"DEB","long":"Debian/Ubuntu package","tool":"dpkg -i"},"sums":[{"algo":"BLAKE3","sum":"f85d98c460c6834ae0ddddfc74061fd8629597dfc1615d41452afb75ef0857a2"},{"algo":"SHA256","sum":"b24ca7916df2cd9f0febb7c32907fd5fa580e6b559eb35eaed97fea4a057f38b"},{"algo":"SHA512","sum":"bd1c8bddb6940c02f25ab912f380d0c6ae3ed8a0cb055f250adc22215e681dd34a5dda2b80790779a3ae372c8a9d2457a4ec0d87800da31fbaf10a07579830aa"}],"cats":["Linux","AArch64","glibc"],"checksum_files":[{"algo":"BLAKE3","url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/v1.25.0/watchexec-1.25.0-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb.b3"},{"algo":"SHA256","url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/v1.25.0/watchexec-1.25.0-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb.sha256"},{"algo":"SHA512","url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/v1.25.0/watchexec-1.25.0-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb.sha512"}]},{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/v1.25.0/watchexec-1.25.0-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.